                        <p className="mt-6 text-base text-[#9a8870] max-w-[520px] leading-relaxed">A comprehensive record of QA leadership and Business Analysis across government sectors in KSA, UAE, and Egypt — from first line of test code to managing enterprise-scale programs.</p>
                        <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-3.5 mt-8">
                            <button onClick={() => navigate("profile")} className="font-bold text-xs px-6 py-3 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors tracking-wider uppercase">← Back to Profile</button>
